{"_id":"darknightveh001","name":"Darknight Venture","type":"vehicle","img":"icons/svg/car.svg","system":{"notes":"<p><strong>Excellent Handling:</strong> When driving a Venture, handling allows the Success Die to be rerolled.</p><p>The Venture also features a hidden holster suitable for most pistols and small SMGs.</p>","skill":"Drive Motorcycle","dimensions":{"length":"2m","width":"1m","height":"0.9m"},"capacity":"1 driver, 1 passenger","mountedWeaponsIgnoreSkillReq":true,"providesCombatCover":true,"hp":{"value":18,"max":18},"armor":{"pv":4,"resist":{"value":14,"max":14}},"move":{"value":30}},"items":[],"effects":[]}
{"_id":"growlervehact001","name":"Growler","type":"vehicle","img":"icons/svg/car.svg","system":{"notes":"<p>Vehicle occupants are considered safe until resistance drops to 0. While using mounted vehicle weapons, the gunner acts in initiative order and ignores normal weapon skill requirements.</p><p>Repairs require correct tools, parts, and downtime.</p>","skill":"Drive (Civilian)","dimensions":{"length":"3.2m","width":"2m","height":"1.7m"},"capacity":"1 driver, 1 passenger","mountedWeaponsIgnoreSkillReq":true,"providesCombatCover":true,"hp":{"value":50,"max":50},"armor":{"pv":4,"resist":{"value":16,"max":16}},"move":{"value":36}},"items":[],"effects":[]}
